  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Forklift Driver",
  "description": "<ul><li>Follow instructions of the Supervisor and ensure that forklift is handled and driven in a proper manner</li><li>Loading & unloading goods in container and lorry</li><li>Ensure proper label on the cargo in and out</li><li>Picking / packing and receiving</li><li>Carry up to 5kg per carton</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned by superior</li><li>Can drive reach truck</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>O-Level / N-Level / NITEC Holder</li><li>Valid forklift licence required</li><li>Min. 2 years' experience in warehouse</li><li>Physically fit</li><li>Friendly, co-operative and good team player</li><li>Outgoing and team orientated personality</li><li>Good communication skills: spoken and written English</li><li>5.5 days work week</li><li>Must be willing to work OT including Public Holidays</li></ul>",
